net.openhft.chronicle.bytes

Interface BytesStore<B extends BytesStore<B,Underlying>,Underlying>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CharSequence, RandomDataInput, RandomDataOutput<B>, net.openhft.chronicle.core.ReferenceCounted
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Bytes<Underlying>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBytes, AbstractBytesStore, GuardedNativeBytes, HeapBytesStore, HexDumpBytes, MappedBytes, MappedBytesStore, NativeBytes, NativeBytes.NativeSubBytes, NativeBytesStore, NoBytesStore, PointerBytesStore, ReadOnlyMappedBytesStore, SubBytes, UncheckedBytes, UncheckedNativeBytes, VanillaBytes

    public interface BytesStore<B extends BytesStore<B,Underlying>,Underlying>
extends RandomDataInput, RandomDataOutput<B>, net.openhft.chronicle.core.ReferenceCounted, CharSequence
    A immutable reference to some bytes with fixed extents. This can be shared safely across thread provided the data referenced is accessed in a thread safe manner. Only offset access within the capacity is possible.
